claim.claim-text:
21. An apparatus for monitoring the condition of a storage battery, comprising: 
battery test circuitry for performing a battery test on the storage battery and providing a battery test result; 
input circuitry receiving subjective information pertaining to the battery; 
calculation circuitry coupled to the battery test circuitry and the input circuitry and generating an audit code based on the battery test result and the subjective information.
